  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  Title: Theatre MIRV
  Description: A multiple independently targetable reentry vehicle (MIRV) is an exoatmospheric
    ballistic missile payload containing several warheads, each capable of being
    aimed to hit a different target. The concept is almost invariably associated
    with intercontinental ballistic missiles carrying thermonuclear warheads, even
    if not strictly being limited to them
